Language::Eforth

This module is a small wrapper for "embed" Forth:

https://github.com/howerj/embed


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands. In particular, the
files embed.c, embde.h, and image.c must first be copied from the embed
repository into the src directory of this module:

  here=`pwd`
  cd somewhere
  git clone https://github.com/howerj/embed
  cp embed/{embed.[ch],image.c} "$here"/src
  cd "$here"
  perl Build.PL
  ./Build
  ./Build test
  ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Language::Eforth


